2011-05-24T07:11:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/british-land-seeks-asset-purchases-in-spain-expansion-reports.html
British Land Co. may focus on  Spain 
as its main area of international growth, and that could
generate a wave of mall acquisitions there,  Expansion  reported,
citing executives of the company.  The British real estate investment trust already owns malls
in the cities of Zaragoza and Toledo, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
